Home page : http://hispider.google.com/p/


Install required
libevbase >= 0.0.11 libsbase >= 0.2.5

download from  http://code.google.com/p/sbase/downloads/
    OR http://sbase.googlecode.com/svn/trunk

Install
    tar -zxf hispider-$ver.tar.gz
    cd hispider-$ver
    ./confgiure --prefix=/$prefix
    make
    make install

Usage
 $prefix/hispider -c $prefix/etc/hispider.ini

